node.text: I personally don’t like to work out my core that much because my muscle memory is unreal & I don’t like “abs” only definition. I also get a good core workout from some of the athletic activities I do on the daily. However y’all have been asking for some core workouts so these are some I do when I need to tighten up ! @cjfitlegend Work at your own pace! #fitness #core
